title: Javor (Serbia)
text: Javor (<a href="Serbian%20Cyrillic">Serbian Cyrillic</a>: Јавор, ) is a <a href="mountains%20of%20Serbia">mountain</a> in southwestern <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>, between towns of <a href="Sjenica">Sjenica</a> and <a href="Ivanjica">Ivanjica</a>. Its highest peak, "Vasilin vrh", has an elevation of 1,519 meters above sea level.
